channel.title: Windows 7 64 bit help
channel.description: Hey everyone I just got a 64 bit laptop and did everything I know to try and run a 317 client but as soon as I run it, javaw.exe in my processes will open then close immediately :mad: Anyone know how to fix this? I have set my environment variables already.

Fixed the problem lol. Me being an idiot and half awake overlooked something. I just started hosting my server again since forever and saw I used a different ip in the client than the newer one I had to remake I’m good to go now.
